name: Liquid Finance
description: Liquid Finance is a cutting-edge liquid staking protocol built on the Archway Network. It enables users to unlock the full potential of their staked assets, allowing for seamless trading, borrowing, and earning of yield without sacrificing staking rewards. With a focus on interoperability and scalability, Liquid Finance revolutionizes staking within the Archway ecosystem, offering a simple and secure solution for liquidity generation..
